configure-azure-cli - Azure CLI Configuration

USAGE:
    configure-azure-cli

DESCRIPTION:
    Configure Azure CLI with automatic updates and authentication.
    Enables auto-upgrade, upgrades CLI, clears accounts, and logs in.

CONFIGURATION:
    -conf-dev-azure-upgrade-timeout SECONDS
        Timeout for upgrade operations

    -conf-dev-azure-login-timeout SECONDS
        Timeout for login operations

    -conf-dev-azure-output-format FORMAT
        Azure CLI output format

EXAMPLES:
    configure-azure-cli
